.container
    .jumbotron.subhead
        %h1
            = @page_title = "Guides"
            %p.lead Packaging Maps for Release
    %section
        .row
            = partial('guides_sidebar')
            .col-sm-9
                .page-header
                    %h1= @page_sub_title = "Cleaning the World Folder"
                :markdown
                    Minecraft will generate quite a few files in your world folder when you create a world. Most of these files are not needed and by deleting them you can reduce the file size when it comes to uploading your world.

                    Below is a table which displays all the files that may be generated in your world folder, along with a description and whether or not the file is required.

                .table-responsive
                    %table.table.table-striped.table-condensed
                        %thead
                            %tr
                                %th File Name
                                %th Required?
                                %th Description
                        %tbody
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code level.dat
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-success YES
                                %td Stores global information about the world such as name and generation type
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code region/
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-success YES
                                %td Contains all the region files of your world
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code data/map_[#].dat
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-warning DEPENDS
                                %td Stores map data for craft-able maps -- remove if you are not using custom map items
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code level.dat_mcr
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td A backup of level.dat before the map was converted from the MCRegion world format to Anvil
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code level.dat_old
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td A backup level.dat
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code session.lock
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td A timestamp when the level was last accessed
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code players/
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Contains player.dat files which store the individual states of each player
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code data/villages.dat
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Stores information about Villages in the world
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code DIM-1/ & DIM1/
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Contains all the region files for the Nether and The End
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code stats/
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Contains achievements and other stats
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code ##MCEDIT.TEMP##/
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Generated by MCEdit
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code forcedchunks.dat
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Forced chunks
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code customnpcs
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Generated by MCEdit/NBTEdit
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code NEI
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Generated by Not Enough Items
                            %tr
                                %td
                                    %code spc
                                %td
                                    %span.label.label-danger NO
                                %td Generated by Single Player Commands
